                <h2>How to Use a Digital Luggage Scale?</h2>
                <p><b>Prepare Your Luggage:</b> Fully pack your bag and zip it up.</p>
                <p><b>Attach the Scale:</b> Secure the bag handle to the scale’s hook or strap.</p>
                <p><b>Lift and Measure:</b> Hold the scale by its handle and lift the bag until it is off the ground. Wait for the weight to stabilize and display on the screen.</p>
                <p><b>Adjust if Necessary:</b> If the weight exceeds the limit, remove or redistribute items to avoid fees.</p>
